data.description: Light-filled and inviting home with rocking chair front porch. Beautiful detailing and walnut stained solid oak wide plank floors throughout main level. 2-story foyer opens to elegant over-sized dining room with coffered ceiling and butler''s pantry. Large eat-in kitchen opens to fireside family room. Massive Master Suite with fireside sitting room, stepped trey ceiling, spacious bath with whirlpool tub, large walk-in shower, dual vanities + his and hers walk-in closets. Spacious secondary bedrooms each with large closets. Level backyard & community pool.
